reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars large computer purse
reviews.reviewText: So, I snagged this awesome large computer purse on black friday, and it's been a total game-changer! First off, it's way more stylish than your typical laptop bag – like, it doesn't scream "I'm carrying a computer." The design is chic, and the color is on point, making it perfect for work meetings or just hanging out.The size is a win, too. My 15-inch laptop fits like a glove, and there's still space for all my random stuff. Inside, there are pockets for days – pens, chargers, you name it.It's pretty sturdy, which I love. The padded laptop part keeps my baby safe, and the whole thing just feels well-made. Plus, it's not just a work bag – I use it as my everyday purse. The adjustable straps make it easy to sling over my shoulder, whether I'm heading to the office or a weekend coffee sesh.The little details are cool, too. It's got this subtle style without being too flashy, and the zippers are smooth as butter. Honestly, it's become my sidekick for everything – work, play, you name it. I'm totally loving this stylish and handy addition to my daily grind!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Leather Tote
reviews.reviewText: This purse has a lot of great features about it. First, I like how big it is. The size accommodates laptops, spiral notebooks, and one inch binders. There are slots for pens and pencils, cell phones, and smaller paper notebooks. There are zip pockets and three divided areas inside the purse. The fabric inside the purse is tan, so be careful about leaving your makeup out. It will stain. The tote comes with shoulder straps and a smaller purse.The outside material is durable and looks like stains won't take to it easy. I got the green color, and it is very nice, very rich. The sewing looks great. I didn't see any snags or tears on the threads.I am pleased with this tote.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and Beautiful Laptop Bag
reviews.reviewText: This bag is the best laptop bag I’ve ever owned. It has enough compartments and pockets to keep me organized but not so many I lose stuff. It is durable and the quality is great- it looks way more expensive than it is. It comes with a cute clutch that make it possible for me to carry only the laptop bag to work without a chunky separate purse. At lunch or to run errands, I just slip out the clutch. The green color is simply gorgeous. There’s also a lanyard/key fob tab inside where you can clip in your badge or keys so they’re convenient to reach without digging in your bag. I love this bag!
